# EchoGridSentinel

EchoGridSentinel is a lightweight distributed monitoring tool that performs heartbeat checks on services and triggers alerts when failures occur.

## Features
- Pings multiple endpoints across regions.
- Tracks consecutive failures and timeouts.
- Sends alerts via email or webhook.
- Periodic reporting for dashboards.

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-org/EchoGridSentinel.git
cd EchoGridSentinel
python monitor/ping_loop.py
